maximum_voltage_magnitude_difference, maximum_phase_angle_difference = main(
    buses_csv_0_file_path=csv_0_file_path, buses_csv_1_file_path=
    csv_1_file_path)
assert maximum_voltage_magnitude_difference < 1e-12
assert maximum_phase_angle_difference < 1e-12
pytest.mark.parametrize('csv_0_file_path, csv_1_file_path', [(ROOT_PATH /
    'data' / 'results' /
    'Results HELM DS M1 PV1 case118 1.02 1e-08 buses.csv', ROOT_PATH /
    'data' / 'results' /
    'Results HELM DS M1 PV2 case118 1.02 1e-08 buses.csv'), (ROOT_PATH /
    'data' / 'results' /
    'Results HELM DS M2 PV1 case118 1.02 1e-08 buses.csv', ROOT_PATH /
    'data' / 'results' /
    'Results HELM DS M2 PV2 case118 1.02 1e-08 buses.csv'), (ROOT_PATH /
    'data' / 'results' / 'Results HELM PV1 case118 1.02 1e-08 buses.csv', 
    ROOT_PATH / 'data' / 'results' /
    'Results HELM PV2 case118 1.02 1e-08 buses.csv')], ids=(
    'helm ds m1 pv1/pv2', 'helm ds m2 pv1/pv2', 'helm pv1/pv2'))
